text:
Data on Moderna’s #COVID19 #vaccine looks good:
-large n: 30418 randomized, 7237 >2 months of follow up
-high efficacy: 94.5% overall & 100% in people >65yo, curves diverge after about 10 days
-safe: more side effects w/ placebo than vaccine (4.1 vs 0.2%)
